Why is autum so suck down here? Im missing out on the leaves turning color, the sent of burning wood and leaves, the delicate grey skys, brisk winds and the antisipation for Holloween, Thanksgiving, Christmas, my birthday, and New Years. Its too surreal to actually fell the change down here. With the constant weather, it feels as if Florida chose random days out of the year just to celebrate their holidays. The only thing that reminds me that the world is revoling around the sun is the fact that the days grow shorter. Its not all about the holidays, its about change. Sure I enjoy nice cool breezey nights in Florida. The thing is, I can enjoy that up north for about six months and then enjoy the aesthetics of season change. My two friends who used to live up north that now live here are seeing what I mean. It is getting to them too. I have been living the same two days for two years: Hot or rain. Sad to say but I am actualy excited for hurricane season. Now it seems that I have to stay longer becuase I failed a class for assinine reasons and now I have fallen behind. Great. In lighter news, my hair is falling out. Seriously. I found out the other day while shampooing my hair only to find my hands where covered with soapy suds and strands of my beautiful hair. Stupid heretitary crap. My mother's side of my gene pool has to offer me diabetes, heart disease, male pattern baldness, obesity and spinal problems. On my dad's lovely genetic menu, there is only one dish: Cancer. My friend Ed said it best "Your a perfect canidate for death." Litte does he know he is a perfect canidate for death too. Muawhawhaw. *Lawl* violence. Considering im a "man" now and I will be 22 in Decemeber, I think it is about time I get my legal shit together. Starting with my will. Oh man the things I will request if I die. If your lucky enough to make the cut, and if I croak, you will find out. Well, between now and till the time I die I have one thing to say... GOD, HERE I COME YOU FUCKING RAT

I honestly dont see any hope of happiness or relaxation for the next 3 months. Why cant it be decmeber already? I want to hit up vegas so bad it hurts. Not only that, i could really go for some scotch and a cigar. I cant drink until december. This livejournal bored me, and I think I might quit for good. All it does is cause me to get a bladder infection. In a differnt light, my step mother is due to deliver my brother in about a month. hopefully if she were smart, she would give me the baby and let me train it to be a womanizing killing machine. Time to spread the t-virus and live my fantasy: to be a zombie hunter and eat beef jerky and chilli. xoxoxo (zo-zo-zo, not "hugz n' kissez")

In a nutshell, this is a perfect description of the "WB".

What really erks me about the WB is, there are people in their offices, stitting around a table, and all of them actually agreeing on bad ideas.  For example:  THEIR WHOLE FUCKING NETWORK.  Why not save all the money spent in college and degrees in marketing and R&D and spend it on a gaggle of retards to come up with new ideas for shows. 

I'll start with Buffy.  Now, when the series began, I thought it would have been a cool idea, then I realized I should have blown out that notion out of my head with a bullet.  ANY Movie turned into a TV series is a horrible idea.  It worked in the 80s, when people had talent.  Ghostbusters the cartoon was bad ass.

Back to what I was saying... Buffy started out on the WB starring an array of now pop culture main stram actors like Sarah Michelle Gellar, Alyson Hannigan, and Adam Carolla wannabe Nicholas Brendon.  The plot of Buffy started and ended in the first Buffy movie back in 1992.  How you can streach all that into, what, 88 seasons of worthless steaming bubbling dino shit is beyond me.  SHE SLAYS VAMPIRES, GET OVER IT.  I heard they were going to have Wesley Snipes as a special guest as Blade, and chop off Buffy's tits and use them as his personal candy dishes.  That would rule.  Oh, and if your reading this Alyson Hannigan, I would LOVE to penitrate you with a flute... through your fucking skull. 

One time, In Adobe Photoshop, I actually used the Canadian leaf brush... and I made this poor illustration!

Thanks for accepting a role that was totally pointless and making all 3 movies suck.

7th Heaven.  Shows like these make me wish I were in a comatos stupor for idiotic reasons, like watching the first gigasecond of the show. Is gigasecond even a word?.... It is now...  7th Heaven is like the Brady Bunch, only worse.  Again, how do you make something from bad to worse.  Brady Bunch was the shit in its time at least.  All those kids who live in the house hold should have been beat from the begining.  I'm talking about the characters AND the little shit head actors.  Whats the point of having kids if you cant crack em one in the teeth. Thus rendering any plot for every episode useless.  These Characters remind me of devoted Christians.  I HATE DEVOTED ANYTHING that regards any religion. Fuck, do somethng worthwhile you brain washed robots.  In the show, the characters go through "real life" delemas and accomplish them together as a family. Cute.  Its been done I think about 700 times in Full House.  The father should be an in-the-closet shit eating petifile.  The daughter should be a goth and totally try to sacrafice her siblings. The son should be a bastard Jock who has a girlfriend and openly cheat on her in front of the girlfriend's parents.  And the youngest should be a clepto maniac.  It would be to good to be true. 

Gilmore Girls is just a waist of time and money, and most of all, all if any nourons popped to come up with such a show.  To be honest, i really dont know what the show is about.  it has a ton of women actresses in it, and I have no idea why it isnt on the WE network.  Too much estro dragon for me to handle.  I think i know more about French politics than I do with this show.  Fuck that shite.

Smallville- Superman was created like 60 some odd years ago.  And since then, there have been a gaggle of TV shows, Comics, Spin Offs, Spin Offs from Spin Offs, and Movies.  From what I have gathered from the legacy known as Superman, Lex Luthar is alwasy bald, everyone has kryptonite, and no matter what you do, Clark Kent always finds a way to resurect.  I caught lke 10 min of Smallville the other day, and the episode was about how three witches posess Clark and Lex.  WTF!? Witches!?  Is there no end to this mutany?

Ill just go off an say that Ellan Degeneres is my arch rival and my primary goal in life is to smother her innar organs on my face.  Nothng would make me happier.

So theres an ugly mexican guy called George Lopezm, and he has his own show.  His character, whom is himself (lame) isnt even a fry cook NOR a landscape maintenance slave.  Boo.  Mexicans never get anything.  WB needs to stick with reality.

Your a redneck if you even think about watching Blue Collar TV.  Stop making $20,000 a year and watch something tastfull, like UFC.

The Kid's WB is even worse.  If I ever, EVER caught my kids watching Kid's WB, I'll kill their mother right in front of them with a strawberry Snapple bottle, and force them to eat her remains.  All they ever air for these hooligans are videogame themed cartoons with catchy brainwashing theme songs and plots even has Ernest Hemmingway spin in his grave to the point where light cant escape him. (Old Man in the Sea sucked Hemmingway).  And to make it even worse, click on this link: http://kidswb.warnerbros.com/web/stuff/stuff_display.jsp?id=LON

Attention children, if you watch this, god will kill all cute and fuzzy animals.  This is a spit in the face for like 2 and a half generations of loyal Looney Tunes fans.  Im pretty sure a lot of souls where condemed to hell for this show.  If anyone, Chuck Jones, Bob Clampett, and Friz Freleng have a right to rotate in their graves, bore a hole to the center of the earth, and summon a volcano right where that stupid water tower is.

In conclusion, FACK YOU WB.  I hope you die.  No shred of decentsy or pride is left in that shallow husk of a studio lot.  Burn is hell.  Thats All Folks.

Yeah.  I have been single for a year and a half now.  Since my last relationship till now, I was feeling pretty good.  I was actually enjoying the single life.  I had a good run.  But like bad indigestion, it came out of nowhere:  I felt alone.

I dont understand what triggered it.  I feel empty, but not depressed.  I dont know how to explain it.  I guess all that surpression finally exploded to a thirst that i cannot quench.  It could be the fact I havent played a new game since Resident Evil 4.  I guess video games supress my primative needs for a companion.  

Ah, who am I kidding.  I think I'll beat Eternal Darkness again.

Back in Fort Lauderdale after having a very intresting vacation. It felt like a dream. Seems like I didnt even leave school to go home. I've decided besides school, there is nothing here for me in Florida. NJ and NY have soul, Florida doesnt. My heart belongs up there. Got to see all my friends and more. It was almost like a class reunion. I couldnt believe the faces I saw when I got back. Oh man the things we did: My friend Gabe and I Dueling with fire to celebrated Independence Day. Notice how I compensate more than he does. Mind you, this was 8 days after I got out of the hospital. Im so cool. Oh, and all of you who are still in the dark, the Statue of Liberty belongs to NJ now. Fuck thats ghey. Probably the most disapointed thing I have heard of all year. One last ride-out with the crew before I go under the knife. My boys. Go Danny Woo. NO GIRLS ALLOWED. *tee hee* Last but definatly not least, Frank wearing Ed's Jacket pretending to be Ed... I think. There was much more insanity to be had. I witnessed Frank light his whole hand on fire, that was fucking halarious. The plan was for him to run around the house and greet one of our friends in the front yard. Frank didnt even make 5 feet before he started smacking his hand on the ground. The fucker's hand was totally in blue flames. As we all know, blue flames means business. He also ate a Ritz Cracker on fire. Dont believe me? Take a look at this: See, this is one of the many reasons Frank is Half of Jesus Christ half incarnated. We decided it was best if I had the other half. There was also the usual lesbianism, drama, and all that jazz. It was like having front row seats for a soap opera. Ah man. Good fucking times. Now Im back here, with no one to chill with because all my friends are either working, going to class, or have stupid girlfriends (I dont think the girlfriends themselves are stupid, just the fact my friends have them is stupid). Thats it for now I guess. Oh yeah, I lost another 10 pounds in a course of a week. 37 pounds in 3 weeks. wowzers. I just wish my aches and scars would go away.

I lost 27 pounds in 11 days


<i>Thanks Trimspa!<i/>

This is it. Pre-op directions are to fast 24 hours prior to operation, and take a high potent laxative to "flush" out my system. Spending my last day as a beast on the throne. Monday at approx. 11:15 am, I'll be proded like a scientist play thing. I wont be back until Wednesday afternoon. I wont have my cell on me either, so no one will hear from me until then. Its funny. All week I have been nervous. Today, I feel content. Im going in guns blazing (or what Josh would say: axe swinging). I am sure I'll be in uncomfortable pain, but I am focusing on the end result. I really need to play tennis again! Hopefully, I will be feeling "normal" a couple days after I get back from the clinic. I am just going to take things one at a time. Well people. Its been a good ride. I dont need to ask you to wish me luck, because I know most of you will do it anyway. Cheers! *chugs laxative*

For the first time ever in my 21 years of exsistance, I am actually scared.  The thought that I will never be the same haunts my thoughts every day.  I have seen the reality of things, and I am not sure if I want to be apart of it.  I will be happy with myself, and I'll be more active, and above all else, healthy.  

I have adjusted how I am and it is now appart of who I am.  My attitude toward things might change, but I fear that it will change for the worse.  Wheather I be more cocky or more discusted with other people I have yet to fore see.  My judgement towards people has been, for the most part, have been shallow.  Thats only because I know they have the same attitude toward me.  Lets face it, people just suck so damn much.

Im not talking about my friends.  I am talking about people in general.  I just wish people would treat me the same if I were who I will be in a year from now.  I dont think I can really trust other people anymore. I dont think I will hadle the new attention I will receive, good or bad. 

I have a double edge sword, yet one blade seems more dull and easier to grasp.   I just cant accept the fact that people are going to have a different attitude toward me in the years to come.  I am too used to handling things my own way.  I have established my own social way, and I sure as hell not ready for a change.  I worked with what I got/had. 

I truely am greatful I have chosen the friends I have, and I hope they feel the same about me.  To those selected few, thank you.

It is impossible for me to win.

I dont know what grieves me as of late.  I seem to lost my steam, my ambition, and my passion for being here.  I am greatly homesick, but thats something I can tolerate.  I started to realize I have no necessary talent to make a career of.  Sure, i can give myself to having a great imagination and ideas, but what good is it if i cannot put it on paper.  

I feel my friends i have known here since i stared that faithful october have grown tired or bored of me, so to speak.  I could see why though.  Story of my life it seems.

Mad drama around this place.  Maybe i should start believing that people have auras and energy that affects the way we feel so i can blame my shitty mood on that. This doesnt mean I wont help anyone if i feel they want or need it, but sometimes i need a break.  I will never take that break as long as i am around the people who i care about.

Then theres June 17th.  That day will be the official New Testament of Andrew.  The date keeps creeping ever closer  I fear that this wont work, and my fixation will take the best of me.  I cant allow it to happen.  I let myself down too many times to fuck this thing up.

I have been thinking too much.  I dont know if it is a phase or not.  So many sources that think they know why I am here, or any of us for that matter. Am I here to be the loving passionate person who will shield and help people from anguish and agony to the point where i would sacrifice myself for the person i care about like my cool psychic aunt said i am/was, and that i have to find a balance?  Did I really have prior lives that i experienced due to my mother's hypnosis?  Or was it my brian producing a hallucination that pieced together from miscellaneous experiences and thoughts?  Is this plane of existence really hell, and there is no fiery torturous afterlife?  Is Heaven really a place to be told "go back and get your shit straight"?  Does our energy/soul travel to another universe and exist in a realm we cant even begin to imagine?  Or are we just advanced animals who have primal instincts and needs, and we disguise it with laws and morals.  maybe my problem is that i have no faith, and as a human being having the need worship a higher being or authority, and follow those laws and morals.  Does love exist, and on that note, has anyone actually really experienced it without taking it for granted?*  

I regret reading the bible multiple times. 

I dont know what my fate or destiny is, but i do know i want to have my name left behind when i die either in a history book, a piece of software, or in cement. I dont want the fame, but i want to prove to people i made an impact on the way they think and mostly my life meant something more meaningful other than the funny passionate guy that can beat any video game with his toes.   

*Note- its a rhetorical question... deal with it*
